---
description: Testing conventions for Playwright e2e and Flutter unit tests
globs: **/*.test.ts,**/*.spec.ts,baller_app/test/**
alwaysApply: false
---

## Flutter

```bash
cd baller_app && flutter analyze
cd baller_app && flutter test
```

- Snapshot may lack `baller_app/test/` — add `test/` before widget tests
- Model tests: `Court.fromMap` round-trip using sample `courts` row maps (no production DB)
- Native smoke: `baller_app/ios/RunnerTests/RunnerTests.swift` · `macos/RunnerTests/RunnerTests.swift`
- Mock `SupabaseClient` in unit tests; never hit prod project `vsqd...supabase.co`

## Playwright

- DevDep: root `package.json` → `@playwright/test`
- Run: `npx playwright test` (add `playwright.config.ts` + specs when introducing e2e)
- UI automation MCP: `.cursor/mcp.json` → `browser` server (`@playwright/mcp`)
